    "description": "Fantasista Co., Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, engages in real estate business in Japan. It operates in three segments: Real Estate Business, Healthcare Business, and Clean Energy Business. The company is involved in the ownership, use, purchase, sale, rental, brokerage, management, and operation of real estate; buying, selling, management, consulting, and holding of securities related to the liquidation of assets; and planning, research, design, and construction consulting services related to urban development and planning. It also operates Under Railway Hotel AKIHABARA, a hotel under an elevated railway; and Zosei-kun.AI, an AI application that proposes plot divisions and create soil amount and cost estimates for land development. In addition, the company manufactures, sells, and imports health food and supplements, health-related equipment, cosmetics, and miscellaneous goods, as well as offers catalog mail orders. Further, it provides grid storage batteries and electric vehicle chargers. The company was formerly known as Asia Gate Holdings Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Fantasista Co., Ltd. in January 2024. Fantasista Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 1950 and is headquartered in Minato, Japan."
